\p Neho ebho bhakang ľeha k Čr…®g…®sa bh Čk Čng ľu, bharabhuga, ‚ÄúM Čm Čbhamb…® k Čm Čsarabha!‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 15 Piraato kwa k Čs…®…®ga k Čsambarucha riribhita rya abhaat Č riyo, akabhataz Čr…®ra Bharaabha. Akaswaja abhasirikar…® korereke bhateme Y…®…®su …®m…®zariti, bhakamotema. Ak Čmara akamuhurucha bham Čbhamb…® k Čm Čsarabha.
\s1 Abhasirikar…® bharasiihya Y…®…®su
\r (Mataayo 27:27‚ÄĎ31; Yoohana 19:2‚ÄĎ3)
\p 
\v 16 Abhasirikar…® bhakagega Y…®…®su, bhakaja nawe mwik Čr Č rya Piraato. Bhakabhiringa riribhita ik Čr Č rya abhasirikar…®.
\v 17 Bhakamwibhohya engebho ya zambaraaw…®. Bhakagisa …®k…®r Čng Č cha amahwa, bhakamwibhohya kumutw…®.
\v 18 Bhakatanga komokeerya kwa kusiihya, ‚ÄúMorembe,  Čm Čt…®mi wa Abhayaahudi!‚ÄĚ
\v 19 Bhaar…® bharamotema kumutw…® na rik Čr…® na kumutw…®ra amat…®, bhakamuhigam…®ra kwa kumukumya.
\v 20 Han Č bhaamarir…® kumusiihya, bhakamuruusha engebho ya zambaraaw…® yirya, na kumwibhohya naatu zengebho zaaz…®. Bhakamuhira bham Čbhamb…® k Čm Čsarabha.
\s1 Y…®…®su arabhambwa k Čm Čsarabha
\r (Mataayo 27:32‚ÄĎ44; Ruuka 23:26‚ÄĎ43; Yoohana 19:17‚ÄĎ27)
\p 
\v 21 K Čnz…®ra, bhakarumana n Č  Čm Č Čt Č w Čn Č aar…® ak Čh…®ta k Čr Čbh…®ri kurwa m Čm Čg Čnd Č, iriina ryaz…® Sim Č Čni kurwa Kireene. …Ąm Č Čt Č wuyo aar…® wiis…® Ar…®kizanda na Ruuf Č. Abhasirikar…® bhakam Čhat…®ka agege  Čm Čsarabha gwa Y…®…®su.
\v 22 Bhakahira Y…®…®su han Č haabhirikiirw…® G Črig Č Čta, enzobhooro yaku n…®‚ÄĎk ČK…®hanga chu Umutw…®.
\v 23 Bhakaha Y…®…®su idivaayi y…®n Č bhaasang…®…®n ľy…® n Č  Čm Čt…®,\f + \fr 15:23 \fk …Ąm Čt…® \ft guyo g Črabhirikirwa man…®man…®, bhakamoha ig Čr Č wo okomorega, gwar…® g Čn Č  Čbh Čr Čr Č.\f* nawe ewe akaanga kunywa.
\v 24 Neho bhakam Čbhamba k Čm Čsarabha, na bhakatwana zengebho zaaz…®. Bhakakora ubhwit Č Čri kuhitya w…®…®w…® aragega engebhok…®.
\v 25 Ribhaga r…®n Č bhaam Čbhambir…®, yaar…® …®sa isat Č ritabh Č Čri.
\p 
\v 26 Bhakat Č Čra ig Čr Č w Č  Čm Čsarabha amaand…®k Č g Č  Čbh Čbh…® bhwaz…®, gaar…® garabhuga, ‚Äú\sc …Ąm Čt…®mi wa Abhayaahudi\sc*.‚ÄĚ
\v 27 Bhakam Čbhamba na abhasaakuri bhabh…®r…® k Čm…®sarabha,  Čw Čmw…®  Čr Čbhaara rwaz…® rwu ubhury Č n Č  Čw Čnd…®  Čr Čbhaara rw Č  Čbh Čm Čsi. [
\v 28 Neho gakakunana Amaand…®k Č Amar…®ndu gan Č gakubhuga, ‚ÄúAkabharwa hamw…®mw…® na abhak Čri bha amabh…®.‚ÄĚ\f + \fr 15:28 \xt Rora Isaaya 53:12.\xt*\f*]
\p 
\v 29 Abhaat Č bhan Č bhaar…® bhak Čh…®ta k Čnz…®ra hayo, bhakam Čt Čka, bharasingisha imitw…® jabh Č bharabhuga, ‚ÄúAa! Aw…®, w Čn Č akwasha rihekaaru na kury Čmbaka kuzisik Č isat Č,
\v 30 nang Č, wiituury…® aumwene, wiik…® k Čm Čsarabha!‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 31 Na abhak Čr Č bha abhakuhaani na abhiija bhi imigir Č ja Musa bh Č Čsi hamw…®mw…®, bhakamorega bharabhuga, ‚ÄúAkasabh Čra abhand…®, nawe atak Čt Čra kwisabh Čra umwene!
\v 32 Ang Č, abhugir…® k Čbha newe Kiriisit Č,  Čm Čt…®mi wa Abhiizira…®ri. Nang Č iik…® k Čm Čsarabha, korereke tomorore nu ukumwisirirya.‚ÄĚ Na abhaat Č bhan Č bhaabhambirw…® hamw…®mw…® nawe, bh Č Čsi bhakam Čt Čka.
\s1 Uruku rwa Y…®…®su
\r (Mataayo 27:45‚ÄĎ56; Ruuka 23:44‚ÄĎ49; Yoohana 19:28‚ÄĎ30)
\p 
\v 33 K Čtang…®ra z…®…®sa isaasabha umwise kuhika z…®…®sa kenda, …®kabha ikiirimya kuchar Č ch Čsi.
\v 34 Neho z…®…®sa kenda, Y…®…®su akar…®ra kwiraka ik Čr Č arabhuga, ‚Äú∆ór Č Čyi! ∆ór Č Čyi! Raama sabhakitaani?‚ÄĚ Enzobhooro yaku ni‚ÄĎ‚ÄúMungu waan…®, Mungu waan…®, ndora untigir…®?‚ÄĚ\f + \fr 15:34 \xt Rora Zabhuri 22:1.\xt*\f*
\p 
\v 35 Abhaat Č obhorebhe gat…® wa bhan Č bhiimiiriir…® harya, han Č bhiigwir…® gan Č ak Čgamba, bhakabhuga, ‚ÄúMwigw…® bhamura, arabh…®r…®k…®ra ∆ó…®riya  Čm Čr Č Čt…®r…®ri wa Mungu.‚ÄĚ\f + \fr 15:35 \ft ∆ó…®riya aragambwa han Č k Č k Čbha Abhayaahudi bhaaru bhaar…® bhariisirirya k Čbha ∆ó…®riya atakuur…®, nawe Mungu akamogega k Č Čs…® han Č m Čh Čru na kuja nawe mwisaar Č. Na bhaar…® bhariisega k Čbha ∆ó…®riya aragar Čka kwik…® k Č Čs…®. \xt Rora 2 Abhat…®mi 2:11; Maraaki 4:5.\xt*\f*
\v 36 …Ąm Č Čt Č w Čmw…® akaryara bhwang Č kotobheka ripuupya m Čmarwa amar Čr Č gi idivaayi, akabhohera kwik Čr…® rir…®…®hu. Akar…®n Čnga ig Čr Č, akaha Y…®…®su anyw…®. …Ąm Č Čt Č wuyo akabhuga, ‚ÄúMutig…® torore ar…®…®bh…® ∆ó…®riya araaza kumwicha k Čm Čsarabha hayo!‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 37 Y…®…®su akar…®ra kwiraka ik Čr Č, akatin ľya.
\v 38 Ripaziya ryu ukusik…®ra Ahar…®ndu ha Ahar…®ndu mwihekaaru\f + \fr 15:38 \fk Ripaziya ryu ukusik…®ra Ahar…®ndu ha Ahar…®ndu mwihekaaru \ft riyo ryar…® mwihekaaru, r…®rak…®nga abhaat Č bhatasik…®ra Ahar…®ndu ha Ahar…®ndu, han Č ubhw…®r Č bhwa Mungu bhwik…®…®r…®. \xt Rora Abh…®…®bhuraaniya 6:19, 10:19‚ÄĎ22. \xt*\ft K Čmarag…®r…®ra bh Čk Čng ľu, rora ring ľana \ft \it rihekaaru\it* muKiniibhasa.\f* r…®kabhaar Čka, mbaara ibh…®r…® kuhika iyaas…®.\fig Ripaziya r…®bhaarukir…® mwihekaaru|alt="Pazia limepasuka hekaluni" src="lb00265c.tif" size="col" loc="MRK 15:38" copy="Louise Bass ¬© The British & Foreign Bible Society, 1994" ref="15:38"\fig*
\v 39 …Ąm Čk Čr Č wa abhasirikar…® w Čn Č aar…® imiiriir…® embere wa Y…®…®su, han Č aar Č Čz…® ch…®mbu Y…®…®su akukwa, akabhuga, ‚ÄúHeene  Čm Č Čt Č w Čn Č aar…® Umwana wa Mungu!‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 40 Bhaareho abhakari bhan Č bhaar Č Čz…® kwa kore. Gat…® waabh Č aareho Mariyamu wa Magidarena, Saroome na Mariyamu unina Yaakobho umusuuhu na Yoose.
\v 41 Abhakari bhayo bhaar…® bhamutunir…® na kohokerya Y…®…®su han Č aar…® muchar Č cha Gariraaya. Bhaareho na abhakari abhand…® bhaaru bhan Č bhagiir…® hamw…®mw…® nawe Y…®rusar…®…®mu.
\s1 Y…®…®su arabhiikwa
\r (Mataayo 27:57‚ÄĎ61; Ruuka 23:50‚ÄĎ56; Yoohana 19:38‚ÄĎ42)
\p 
\v 42 Han Č ryahikir…® rigoroobha, k Č k Čbha urusik Č ruyo rwar…® rwu ukwit Č Čra bhwaheene, ig Čr Č wu urusik Č rw Č  Čbh Čt Č Čr Č,\f + \fr 15:42 \fk …Ąbh Čt Č Čr Č \ft bh Čkatanga han Č iry Čbha ryatubhiir…® Ijumaa kuhika han Č ryatubhiir…® Jumam Č Čsi. Amaswaja ga Abhayaahudi gatakwisirirya k Čbh…®…®ka  Čm Č Čt Č urusik Č rw Č  Čbh Čt Č Čr Č.\f*
\v 43 akaaza  Čm Č Čt Č w Čmw…® w Čn Č akubhirikirwa Yuusufu, umwibhurwa w Č  Čr Čbh…®ri rwa Arimataaya. Aar…® wu ubhusuuku bh Čk Čng ľu, wa muchandar Č …®k…®k Čr Č cha Abhayaahudi, na aar…® ariisega  Čbh Čt…®mi bhwa Mungu bh Čn Č bhukuuza. Akaja kwa Piraato kwa bh Čkaari k Čm Čsabha amwisiririry…® aj…® agege …®k…®t Čnd Č cha Y…®…®su.
\p 
\v 44 Han Č Piraato iigwir…® k Čbha bhwang Čbhu Y…®…®su akuur…®, akar Čg Č Čra! Akam Čbh…®r…®k…®ra  Čm Čk Čr Č wa abhasirikar…® wurya korereke amenyeekererye ar…®…®bh…® maheene Y…®…®su akuur…®.
\v 45 Han Č aam…®ny…®…®k…®r…®…®ry…® k Čbha Y…®…®su akuur…®, Piraato akiisiririrya Yuusufu agege …®k…®t Čnd Č.
\v 46 Neho Yuusufu w Č Čsi akag Čra …®sanda ya zimpirya nzaru. Akiicha …®k…®t Čnd Č kurwa k Čm Čsarabha, akakiring…®ra n…® …®sanda. Akabh…®…®ka …®k…®t Čnd Č kirya mumbih…®ra y…®n Č yaak…®r…®sirw…® kwitar…®, akahiringitya riibhw…® ik Čr Č na kuribha kukisik Č chi imbih…®ra.
\v 47 Na Mariyamu wa Magidarena na Mariyamu unina Yaakobho musuuhu na Yoose, bhakarora han Č aabhiikirw…®.
\c 16
\s1 Y…®…®su arary Čka
\r (Mataayo 28:1‚ÄĎ8; Ruuka 24:1‚ÄĎ12; Yoohana 20:1‚ÄĎ10)
\p 
\v 1 Han Č urusik Č rw Č  Čbh Čt Č Čr Č rwahitir…®, Mariyamu wa Magidarena, Saroome na Mariyamu unina Yaakobho, bhakag Čra amaguta go okoreetya, bhaj…® bhahak…® …®k…®t Čnd Č.
\v 2 Urusik Č rw Č  Čbh Čtang…® rwi inyuma\f + \fr 16:2 \fk Urusik Č rw Č  Čbh Čtang…® rwi inyuma \ft k ČBhayaahudi ni‚ÄĎJumapiri.\f* ritabh Č Čri, han Č iry Čbha ryatangir…® kosomoka, bhakaja kumbih…®ra ya Y…®…®su.
\v 3 Han Č bhaar…® m Čnz…®ra, bhakatanga kwibhuurya, ‚ÄúN…®‚ÄĎw…®…®w…® w Čn Č akuturuushirya riibhw…® rirya kukisik Č chi imbih…®ra?‚ÄĚ
\v 4 Nawe han Č bhaahikir…®, bhakarora riibhw…® rirya rihiringitiibhw…®, riri rusiz Č, na ryar…® ik Čr Č bh Čk Čng ľu.
\p 
\v 5 Han Č bhaasikiir…® mumbih…®ra, bhakiitacha korora mumura w Čmw…® ibh Čhir…® engebho nz…®r Č. Iik…®…®r…®  Čr Čbhaara rwu ubhury Č rwi imbih…®ra.
\v 6 Neho akabhabh Č Čr…®ra, ‚ÄúM Čt Č Čbhaha! N…®…®z…® m Čramohya Y…®…®su wa Nazar…®…®ti, w Čn Č aabhambirw…®. Atar…® han Č! Aryukir…®, morore han Č bhaam Čt…®…®r…®.
\v 7 Muj…® m Čbh Č Čr…®r…® abh…®…®ga bhaaz…®, k…®nda Peetero k Čbha, Y…®…®su arabhakangat…®ra kuja Gariraaya. Iyo neyo m Čraamorore ch…®mbu aabhabhuuriir…®.‚ÄĚ\f + \fr 16:7 \xt Rora Maaroko 14:28.\xt*\f*
\v 8 Han Č bhiigwir…®bhu, bhakatanga kurigita kwa bhw Čbha na k Čr Čg Č Čra. Bhakarwa mumbih…®ra hayo mwega. Bhataabhuuriir…® m Č Čt Č w Čw Č Čsi, k Č k Čbha bhak Č Čbhaha.
\s1 Y…®…®su arahwar Čk…®ra Mariyamu wa Magidarena
\r (Mataayo 28:9‚ÄĎ10; Yoohana 20:11‚ÄĎ18)
\p [
\v 9 Han Č Y…®…®su aaryukir…® ritabh Č Čri urusik Č rw Č  Čbh Čtang…® rwi inyuma, akamuhwar Čk…®ra hinga Mariyamu wa Magidarena, w Čn Č aar…® amuruushiry…® amasambwa muhungat…®.
\v 10 Mariyamu akaja, akabhabh Č Čr…®ra bhan Č bhaar…® hamw…®mw…® na Y…®…®su, na ribhaga riyo bhaar…® bharar…®ra na kwarama.
\v 11 Nawe han Č bhiigwir…® k Čbha Mariyamu akamorora m Čh Čru, bhatiisiriiry…®.
\s1 Y…®…®su arabhahwar Čk…®ra abh…®…®ga bhabh…®r…®
\r (Ruuka 24:13‚ÄĎ35)
\p 
\v 12 Urusik Č ruyoruyo, Y…®…®su akahwar Čk…®ra abh…®…®ga bhaaz…® bhabh…®r…®, aar…® ni ikisisi k…®nd…®. Abh…®…®ga bharya bhaar…® k Čnz…®ra bhararwa Y…®rusar…®…®mu.
\v 13 Bh Č Čsi bhakagar Čka k Čbhabh Č Čr…®ra abhak…®ndichabh Č, nawe abh…®…®ga bhayo bhatiisiriiry…®.
\s1 Y…®…®su arahwar Čk…®ra abh…®…®ga bhaaz…®
\r (Mataayo 28:16‚ÄĎ20; Ruuka 24:36‚ÄĎ49; Yoohana 20:19‚ÄĎ23; Amahocha ga Abhatumwa 1:6‚ÄĎ8)
\p 
\v 14 M Čt…®n…®r Č, Y…®…®su akahwar Čk…®ra abh…®…®ga bhaaz…® ikumi na w Čmw…®, han Č bhaar…® kwigari bhararya. Akabharecha k Čbh Čk Čng ľu bhwi imy Čy Č jabh Č, k Č k Čbha bhaangir…® kwisirirya ga abhak…®ndichabh Č bhan Č bhaar Č Čz…® Y…®…®su han Č aaryukir…® m Čbhaku.
\v 15 Neho akabhabh Č Čr…®ra, ‚ÄúMuj…® mubhyar Č bhy Čsi, m Čbharwaz…®r…® abhaat Č bh Č Čsi ∆óng ľana yaan…® ∆ónz Čmu.
\v 16 W Čn Č w Č Čsi ariisiriry…® na k Čbhatiizwa, arasabhurwa. Nawe, w Čn Č araang…® kwisirirya, aratinirwa.
\v 17 Abhaat Č bhan Č bhariisiriry…®, bharakora ibhy…®r…®k…®n ľy Č bh…®n Č, ukuruusha amasambwa k Čbhaat Č kuriina ryan…®,  Čk Čgamba …®bh…®gamb Č ibhihya,
\v 18 bhangagwata nzoka hamw…® bhanganywa kegero cha kwita, k…®tak Čbhanyahaara. Bharabha bharat Č Čra amabhoko gaabh Č k Čbharw…®r…®, bh Č Čsi bharahora.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Y…®…®su aragegwa kuja mwisaar Č
\r (Ruuka 24:50‚ÄĎ53; Amahocha ga Abhatumwa 1:9‚ÄĎ11)
\p 
\v 19 Han Č …Ąm Čk Čr Č Y…®…®su aamarir…® k Čgambana nabh Č, Mungu akamogega kuja mwisaar Č. Akiikara  Čr Čbhaara rwu ubhury Č rwa Mungu.
\v 20 Abh…®…®ga bhaaz…® bharya bhakabh Č Čka, bhakaja kurwaza ∆óng ľana ∆ónz Čmu hagero h Č Čsi. …Ąm Čk Čr Č Y…®…®su aar…® arabhaha amanaga go okokora ibhy…®r…®k…®n ľy Č. N…®mbu aar…® aramenyeekererya amang ľana gayo k Čbha n…®‚ÄĎga amaheene.]
